fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一諗翻起或者夢見佢就會喊翻，依家就無成日諗啦<br />\n<br />\n加油啊，頭一兩個月真係好難過，特別係搞儀式個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdadf0e78eab180247ac2660b2b16b3af1b9cc6d","tid":1021193,"uid":135957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T13:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63f40ef4d09607201322091286a4be48eeb2022b","tid":1021193,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49c2028ad78c84631b78fc9d6fb63f8f4ce0e43c","tid":1021193,"uid":130365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T13:02:45.000Z","msg":"因咩事.. cancer?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T13:11:24.000Z","msg":"應該係心有事"},{"pid":"eadfe31c935119c67519c3eb2f0763a256b59581","tid":1021193,"uid":224290,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T13:25:12.000Z","msg":"兩三年左右 一開始係會無啦啦都可以流眼淚 啊爺走左5年 諗返起佢都係會想喊 但唔會再好似以前個心嗱住嗱住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前排係ig見到條片講個孫影低左爺爺每次見到佢個開心樣 喊到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好掛住啊爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8547d48165468301769c43228e291fb09362df","tid":1021193,"uid":28037,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T13:31:47.000Z","msg":"2年幾<br />\n<br />\n爸爸走咗之後個人沉咗好耐唔想讀書唔想返工咩都唔想做 只係沉醉係悲傷之中<br />\n<br />\n後來都係決定讀返書 生活有其他事情去依賴一下 先慢慢淡忘悲傷嘅情感<br />\n<br />\n走出咗悲傷情緒 唔代表對家人思念都無埋嘅<br />\n永遠爸爸係自己心中都佔有一席位"},{"pid":"9f948077b7c1b981173c04867ad34fd7d3ef0e45","tid":1021193,"uid":198204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T13:36:58.000Z","msg":"借問聲走咗幾耐<br />\n樓主 take care <br />\n間屋都係得我同爸爸一齊住 我同佢關係都麻麻<br />\n有時嫌佢烏嘈 唔趕淨 文失 <br />\n以後會對佢好啲 珍惜時間"},{"pid":"37f63b7592b89b530e6312bb7f2dfd78cc2cfc96","tid":1021193,"uid":229391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T13:51:28.000Z","msg":"唔會完全走得出<br />\n只希望你可以好好處理傷口<br />\n有唔開心要揾人傾訴 嘗試分散下注意力<br />\n做一啲嘢去紀念佢 例如做義工，用佢個名捐錢幫人<br />\n延續佢嘅愛，亦從中做更好嘅自己<br />\n知道你一啲都唔容易 但加油啊，你一定做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2e7497bc573a1192bca36c535c73da14c8e8bb","tid":1021193,"uid":196964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:06:59.000Z","msg":"去個旅行 可能可以減輕一點傷痛"},{"pid":"65cb017e3c2f7021dc78e147fc2b9e928883714b","tid":1021193,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"睇下一套紀錄片叫伴生"},{"pid":"ec1cfedc74a9a9f8d504e8463e9fa5531371ca6c","tid":1021193,"uid":200117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:31:14.000Z","msg":"兩年先接受到件事<br />\n但間中都會記返起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9500fb6b750b8137a1cde5a469179f3a6350be","tid":1021193,"uid":176179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:33:01.000Z","msg":"好明白個種感受，依個傷痛真係因人而異。<br />\n就算過左一年，上山探佢都忍唔住留幾滴眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5bf03799f33fb403878740dbe55b3a6509463c","tid":1021193,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0b84aee14b2476141623c826d1f1084e29d4b927","tid":1021193,"uid":21423,"like":15,"dislike":56,"score":-41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"咁你推你老母做雞、幫你老竇執骨嗰陣又係點心情？"},{"pid":"01338c970949d08036423283783b066b22c0a5d9","tid":1021193,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:34:36.000Z","msg":"Time will help"},{"pid":"9323b9b4f439797cd140a5091a7d873348a55646","tid":1021193,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:35:21.000Z","msg":"樓主節哀，相信你爸爸喺天堂都唔想見到你終日愁眉苦面，好好珍惜其他人，好好生活，去愛佢同長留喺心中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d10057421e41af312df3b88d4ba63fcfa1727d","tid":1021193,"uid":41888,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:43:33.000Z","msg":"巴打 你有個錫你既呀爸 難免需要長D時間走出傷痛<br />\n搵D野學下 做下運動<br />\n要明白生老病死 人總有一死 你同我遲早都會 只係自然既過程<br />\n唔需要太過自責<br />\n<br />\n我呀爸係個食煙飲酒奶共廢中 全家人都黑佢憎 <br />\n佢鼻咽癌死左之後 我都掛住左佢幾個月<br />\n<br />\n但慢慢明白其實佢死左對社會同屋企都係好事 諗通左之後就無咩野了"},{"pid":"20cb988d4346848157d4ca13bc88bc48e04d6816","tid":1021193,"uid":36329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"我淨係想像我老豆走已經想喊<br />\n巴打肯定好難受<br />\n唔好死頂 想喊就喊"},{"pid":"d01e6db2b493694278859354c03560ed370f7ff0","tid":1021193,"uid":22656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"51a00b885b856dd4abd648eec7ac1d8be7f211e6","tid":1021193,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"076a2101f7ebb0e908430b513eee946290397fdb","tid":1021193,"uid":22656,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:05:51.000Z","msg":"加油💪🏻 我都努力中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T13:01:39.000Z","msg":"屋企裡面一望到阿爸既物件/衣服，個腦就會諗起好多畫面，間中又會諗起阿爸把聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"我明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我爸上個月突然間走左，而家有時返返下工會無端端流淚，行行下街搭巴士港鐵睇到舊相又會眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又唔可以同屋企人講，因為大家都難受<br />\n唯有暱埋係廁所沖涼嗰陣喊下會舒服啲<br />\n<br />\n巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806fd1e278bd794d02db31d0ff685c8430e13fb2","tid":1021193,"uid":224827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc0e694a8e13ca975882d848280402c70a968110","tid":1021193,"uid":49643,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a99422af0bbd99f1121d29cb14bec5aad726fdcb","tid":1021193,"uid":224827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"唔同人真係唔同 有啲人可能真係一路都走唔出<br />\n所以好需要去搵啲方法舒發下感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T13:07:24.000Z","msg":"個心好難受，雖然我地住埋一齊，但係關係又唔算好親近，可能工作，其他原因，以前問我野都係敷衍咁答佢，近幾年好似忽略左阿爸咁，我覺得自己好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T15:08:14.000Z","msg":"巴打呀爸係咩事離世呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時候就算關係有幾差或者有幾好都會有唔開心 因為終於係一家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e14c95c4369128b137fefe354a450e70d68516","tid":1021193,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"806fd1e278bd794d02db31d0ff685c8430e13fb2","tid":1021193,"uid":224827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc0e694a8e13ca975882d848280402c70a968110","tid":1021193,"uid":49643,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a99422af0bbd99f1121d29cb14bec5aad726fdcb","tid":1021193,"uid":224827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"唔同人真係唔同 有啲人可能真係一路都走唔出<br />\n所以好需要去搵啲方法舒發下感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T13:07:24.000Z","msg":"個心好難受，雖然我地住埋一齊，但係關係又唔算好親近，可能工作，其他原因，以前問我野都係敷衍咁答佢，近幾年好似忽略左阿爸咁，我覺得自己好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T15:08:14.000Z","msg":"巴打呀爸係咩事離世呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\